originalText.text: Love this place! Darryl has such a positive attitude and is always in a good mood, on top of being a great trainer. I’ve never had a personal trainer before and in just a few months, I can literally feel how the shape of my body is changing for the better. The gym is very welcoming and clean - 10/10 would recommend!

originalText.text:
How you treat a stranger says a great deal about a person…

I was parking my vehicle in front of this gentleman’s vehicle & he went outside his Fitness Studio to make sure I didn’t bump into his car, he gave me that look and no problem lol. After I parked, I explained to him i have OCD parking and it was a new vehicle for me to operate and he was so respectful and cool about it.

Listen i get it, its nyc and sometimes we have to be protective of our vehicle and this man was multitasking training someone and watching his car. The reason im giving 5 stars is because he made me want to join his studio because he knows how to treat people with respect. And His gym looks clean, organized and professional. Sign up.

originalText.text: Great full body workout tailored to my needs with a well informed and certified trainer.  Excellent facility that is super clean, well equipped and not crowded.  Highly recommend for those who want a trainer supervised program outside of the hustle and bustle of the gym.  Well priced for such a personal program with 1-1 attention.
